high_descs: Go to the white table ahead of you, in front of the window.
Pick up the yellow knife on the front of the table.
Turn around and go across the kitchen to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the knife, turn the water off, and remove the knife from the sink.
Turn around and go back to the white table across from you.
Place the knife on the front, left corner of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on the table.
